marketing: Shell Helix Ultra AV-L is the latest-generation, fully synthetic engine oil designed specifically to provide the ultimate engine protection for almost all Volkswagen, Audi, Škoda and SEAT gasoline and diesel engines, including those with diesel particulate filters. It is approved by these manufacturers for normal and extended service.
